=== Sustainable transport activism ===

Wikipedia: [[wikipedia:Tammany Trace|Tammany Trace]]: rail trail in Louisiana occupying a former Illinois Central Railroad corridor. It has been developed into a 31-mile (50 km) asphalt trail for hiking, [[cycling]], and wheelchair use with a parallel equestrian trail. It connects Covington, Abita Springs, Mandeville, Lacombe, and Slidell running along the northshore of Lake Pontchartrain.

